[@ image("UBC-DYN-18-072.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

Find the angular velocity of rod [`AB`] using rotating frame relative motion analysis.   

[`\overrightarrow{\Omega_{AB}} =`] [_____]{"$wab"} [`rad/s`]  

END_PGML



